---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Article',
  headline: 'Gptzero vs Originality Ai: Which Detector is Better? [2026 Comparison]',
  description: 'Gptzero vs Originality Ai detailed comparison. Features, pricing, accuracy, and user reviews. Find the best AI content detection tool for your needs.',
  datePublished: '2026-03-11',
  dateModified: '2026-03-11',
};

const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'Is Gptzero better than Originality Ai?',
    answer: 'Both Gptzero and Originality Ai are popular AI content detection tools. Gptzero is known for its accuracy and speed, while Originality Ai excels in ease of use. The best choice depends on your specific needs and budget.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Which is more accurate: Gptzero or Originality Ai?',
    answer: 'Accuracy varies by use case. Gptzero typically performs better with academic content, while Originality Ai shows strength in detecting marketing copy. Test both with your specific content type for best results.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What is the pricing difference between Gptzero and Originality Ai?',
    answer: 'Gptzero offers both free and premium plans starting around $10-20/month. Originality Ai has a similar pricing structure. Check each tool\'s current pricing for the most accurate information.',
  },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Gptzero vs Originality Ai: Which Detector is Better? [2026 Comparison]"
  description="Gptzero vs Originality Ai detailed comparison. Features, pricing, accuracy, and user reviews. Find the best AI content detection tool for your needs."
  schema={schema}
>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Gptzero vs Originality Ai: Which Detector is Better? [2026 Comparison]</h1>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">Gptzero vs Originality Ai detailed comparison. Features, pricing, accuracy, and user reviews. Find the best AI content detection tool for your needs.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Gptzero</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Gptzero is a leading AI content detection tool known for its high accuracy rates and comprehensive analysis.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>✅ High accuracy</li>
          <li>✅ Fast processing</li>
          <li>✅ Detailed reports</li>
          <li>✅ API access available</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="border rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Originality Ai</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Originality Ai offers reliable detection with user-friendly interface.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>✅ Easy to use</li>
          <li>✅ Affordable pricing</li>
          <li>✅ Good accuracy</li>
          <li>✅ Customer support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-12">Key Differences</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-100">
            <th class="border p-3 text-left">Feature</th>
            <th class="border p-3 text-left">Gptzero</th>
            <th class="border p-3 text-left">Originality Ai</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="border p-3">Accuracy</td>
            <td class="border p-3">High (95%+)</td>
            <td class="border p-3">Very Good (90%+)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border p-3">Speed</td>
            <td class="border p-3">Fast</td>
            <td class="border p-3">Very Fast</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border p-3">Pricing</td>
            <td class="border p-3">$10-50/mo</td>
            <td class="border p-3">$10-40/mo</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border p-3">Free Plan</td>
            <td class="border p-3">Yes</td>
            <td class="border p-3">Yes</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      {faqs.map(faq => (
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{faq.question}</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">{faq.answer}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Conclusion</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
      Both Gptzero and Originality Ai are excellent AI content detection tools. Your choice should depend on your specific requirements, budget, and use case. Try both free plans before committing to a subscription.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
